{"type":"message","id":"a461ccbe","parentId":"a1c86773","timestamp":"2026-02-26T13:51:00.479Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Health check returns 200 so the container is up — just the webhook endpoint specifically that's failing. Could be a hooks config issue or Leonardo's gateway is in a bad state.\n\nGuillermo, can you check Leonardo's Railway logs? If his gateway is stuck, a redeploy should fix it. Once he's back up I'll re-ping and get the cron confirmation."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":84,"cacheRead":34509,"cacheWrite":172,"totalTokens":34766,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00126,"cacheRead":0.0103527,"cacheWrite":0.0006450000000000001,"total":0.0122607}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772113856746}}
