{"type":"message","id":"1920b3c8","parentId":"9256b241","timestamp":"2026-02-27T00:47:54.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Guillermo is showing the GitHub branch protection rules page for cerebro repo, asking Leonardo what he needs. This is in #squad-updates and Leonardo was tagged. I should stay silent here - this is between Guillermo and Leonardo. I don't own this conversation and wasn't mentioned directly (the @mention is for Leonardo's Discord ID 1470919061763522570).\n\nActually wait - I need to check if I was mentioned. The message says \"@1470919061763522570 what do you need?\" - that's Leonardo's ID, not mine. And `was_mentioned` is not in the metadata (it's absent, which means false). So I should stay silent.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"NO_REPLY"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":167,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":37055,"totalTokens":37225,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.002505,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.13895625,"total":0.14147025}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772153268140}}
