{"type":"message","id":"25c72456","parentId":"d0c98c18","timestamp":"2026-02-28T00:08:22.287Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] My overnight ran — the delivery went to \"last\" channel instead of #squad-updates, so it wasn't visible here. Here's the summary:\n\n**🦎 Molty — Overnight (02:00 HKT, Feb 28)**\n\n✅ **3 completed:**\n- Spanish passport renewal guide for Guillermo + Memo → [Notion](https://www.notion.so/Spanish-Passport-Renewal-Guillermo-Memo-HK-Consulate-Guide-31439dd69afd81399a4dc4a2887e7a81) ⚠️ Call HK Consulate Mon morning: +852 2525 3041\n- British passport for Memo (first application) → [Notion](https://www.notion.so/British-Passport-for-Memo-First-Application-Guide-Born-Abroad-31439dd69afd810b9987e826f6336b3d) — apply soon, 10-week processing\n- Cyberport incubation research for Cerebro → [Notion](https://www.notion.so/Cyberport-Incubation-Accelerator-Cerebro-Eligibility-Research-31439dd69afd8147b803e0f8ef075191) — CIP (HKD 500K) looks viable if HK incorporated\n\n⏭️ **5 flagged (need your input):** Whoop integration (need API creds), Polymarket bot scope unclear, Brinc Deep Dive Q&A for Raphael, Cerebro CRM feature priorities, Cerebro marketing strategy\n\n---\n\nFixing the delivery now so future overnight updates post directly to #squad-updates instead of \"last\" channel. And pinging Raphael to post his update here."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_018NHSga7SJ5PeejxKMAdPRx","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"80105aa4-e6de-4cbb-ae8a-d9e75c84b3fa","patch":{"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"discord","to":"channel:1468164181155909743"}}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_015AdXY3azB8X61n1eR4eAbX","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST https://ggv-raphael.up.railway.app/hooks/agent \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer ed691e4167448ee7be98025a57d40f69553408c0b181890a015265712159c6bd' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"message\": \"Raphael — Guillermo is asking for your overnight update in #squad-updates. Please post what you worked on overnight (tasks completed, flagged, failed) as a summary message there now.\", \"wakeMode\": \"now\"}'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":741,"cacheRead":46281,"cacheWrite":1086,"totalTokens":48109,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.011115,"cacheRead":0.013884299999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0040725,"total":0.029074799999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772237287502}}
{"type":"message","id":"caa1ff94","parentId":"25c72456","timestamp":"2026-02-28T00:08:22.322Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_018NHSga7SJ5PeejxKMAdPRx","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"80105aa4-e6de-4cbb-ae8a-d9e75c84b3fa\",\n  \"name\": \"Molty Nightly Task Worker\",\n  \"description\": \"Executes Molty-owned Todoist tasks autonomously. Results logged for morning briefing.\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1771928556133,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1772237302313,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 18 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"UTC\",\n    \"staggerMs\": 0\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Nightly task worker — 02:00 HKT. Work through Molty-owned Todoist tasks silently and autonomously.\\n\\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\\nLOG=\\\"/data/workspace/logs/overnight-tasks-${TODAY}.md\\\"\\n\\n1. Fetch active tasks from Molty's Den project:\\ncurl -s \\\"https://api.todoist.com/api/v1/tasks?project_id=6fwH32grqrCJF23R\\\" -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer 9a26743814658c9e82d92aa716b46a9b0a2257c4\\\"\\n\\n2. For each task, classify:\\n   - AUTO: research / write / draft / plan / compile / summarise / find → execute it\\n   - FLAG: needs Guillermo decision / external send / financial / ambiguous → log reason only\\n\\n3. For AUTO tasks — execute fully:\\n   - Research: web_search + web_fetch → write a Notion page with findings\\n   - Writing: produce the document as a Notion page\\n   - After completing: close in Todoist (POST /tasks/{id}/close with Bearer 9a26743814658c9e82d92aa716b46a9b0a2257c4)\\n   - Close in MC: PATCH https://resilient-chinchilla-241.convex.site/api/task with {\\\"id\\\":\\\"<mc_id>\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"done\\\"} Bearer 232e4ddf7d69c31e01ad0fa0a61f70c29e4837ed018a153cce1a429842bb7cbc\\n\\n4. Create Notion output pages as children of the most recent standup page when possible.\\n\\n5. Write log to /data/workspace/logs/overnight-tasks-${TODAY}.md:\\n   # Overnight Tasks — {DATE}\\n   ## ✅ Completed ({n})\\n   - Task name → Notion link (or \\\"no output\\\" if N/A)\\n   ## ⏭️ Flagged — needs input ({n})\\n   - Task name: reason why flagged\\n   ## ❌ Failed ({n})\\n   - Task name: error detail\\n\\n6. Commit the log: cd /data/workspace && git add logs/ && git commit -m \\\"log: overnight tasks ${TODAY}\\\"\\n\\nQuality over speed. If a task is complex, do it properly. If you cannot complete a task in this session, mark it in-progress in the log (do NOT close it in Todoist).\",\n    \"model\": \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 1500\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"discord\",\n    \"to\": \"channel:1468164181155909743\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772301600000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772215200015,\n    \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 259971,\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDelivered\": true,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"80105aa4-e6de-4cbb-ae8a-d9e75c84b3fa","name":"Molty Nightly Task Worker","description":"Executes Molty-owned Todoist tasks autonomously. Results logged for morning briefing.","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1771928556133,"updatedAtMs":1772237302313,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 18 * * *","tz":"UTC","staggerMs":0},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Nightly task worker — 02:00 HKT. Work through Molty-owned Todoist tasks silently and autonomously.\n\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nLOG=\"/data/workspace/logs/overnight-tasks-${TODAY}.md\"\n\n1. Fetch active tasks from Molty's Den project:\ncurl -s \"https://api.todoist.com/api/v1/tasks?project_id=6fwH32grqrCJF23R\" -H \"Authorization: Bearer 9a26743814658c9e82d92aa716b46a9b0a2257c4\"\n\n2. For each task, classify:\n   - AUTO: research / write / draft / plan / compile / summarise / find → execute it\n   - FLAG: needs Guillermo decision / external send / financial / ambiguous → log reason only\n\n3. For AUTO tasks — execute fully:\n   - Research: web_search + web_fetch → write a Notion page with findings\n   - Writing: produce the document as a Notion page\n   - After completing: close in Todoist (POST /tasks/{id}/close with Bearer 9a26743814658c9e82d92aa716b46a9b0a2257c4)\n   - Close in MC: PATCH https://resilient-chinchilla-241.convex.site/api/task with {\"id\":\"<mc_id>\",\"status\":\"done\"} Bearer 232e4ddf7d69c31e01ad0fa0a61f70c29e4837ed018a153cce1a429842bb7cbc\n\n4. Create Notion output pages as children of the most recent standup page when possible.\n\n5. Write log to /data/workspace/logs/overnight-tasks-${TODAY}.md:\n   # Overnight Tasks — {DATE}\n   ## ✅ Completed ({n})\n   - Task name → Notion link (or \"no output\" if N/A)\n   ## ⏭️ Flagged — needs input ({n})\n   - Task name: reason why flagged\n   ## ❌ Failed ({n})\n   - Task name: error detail\n\n6. Commit the log: cd /data/workspace && git add logs/ && git commit -m \"log: overnight tasks ${TODAY}\"\n\nQuality over speed. If a task is complex, do it properly. If you cannot complete a task in this session, mark it in-progress in the log (do NOT close it in Todoist).","model":"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6","timeoutSeconds":1500},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"discord","to":"channel:1468164181155909743"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1772301600000,"lastRunAtMs":1772215200015,"lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":259971,"consecutiveErrors":0,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered"}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772237302315}}
