{"type":"message","id":"82a66d78","parentId":"510ae649","timestamp":"2026-03-02T13:18:19.755Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-02 21:18 GMT+8] [System Message] [sessionId: 3fa52554-cf83-4f0d-8c12-028f982c396d] A cron job \"Fleet Update Check (05:15 HKT)\" just completed successfully.\n\nResult:\n**FLEET UPDATE CHECK COMPLETE — 21:18 HKT**\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**Update Attempted:** v2026.3.1 (CRITICAL — 13 security patches)\n\n### Results\n- **🦎 Molty:** ❌ **Failed** — version mismatch after in-place update (still on v2026.2.26, expected v2026.3.1)\n- **🔴 Raphael:** ✅ Webhook directive sent — Railway redeploy failed (403 Forbidden), fallback to webhook successful\n- **🔵 Leonardo:** ✅ Webhook directive sent — Railway redeploy failed (403 Forbidden), fallback to webhook successful\n\n### Status\n- **Overall:** Partial failure (`molty: failed`, `raphael: ✅`, `leonardo: ✅`)\n- **Raphael & Leonardo:** Version update unconfirmed pending self-report (agents must confirm running v2026.3.1)\n- **Molty:** Requires manual investigation — in-place update did not apply version correctly\n\n### What's New (v2026.3.1)\n- Thread-bound agent Discord sessions (auto-routing to threads)\n- Built-in HTTP health endpoints (`/health`, `/ready`)\n- Android/Nodes: camera.list, device.permissions, notifications.actions\n- Telegram/DM topics: per-DM config with topic routing\n- Web UI cron i18n (English + zh-CN)\n- OpenAI WebSocket-first streaming\n\n### Critical Actions Needed\n1. **Molty version fix:** Check why v2026.3.1 didn't apply — may need manual Railway trigger or restart\n2. **Raphael & Leonardo:** Monitor for self-reported v2026.3.1 confirmation\n3. **Token verification:** Post-update, verify all agent auth tokens are valid (security improvements in this version)\n\n---\n\n**Notifications already sent:**\n- ✅ Discord #command-center (21:18 HKT)\n- ✅ Telegram to Guillermo (21:18 HKT)\n\nStats: runtime 3m19s • tokens 2.0k (in 69 / out 1.9k) •