{"type":"message","id":"b6e912d5","parentId":"cfd91641","timestamp":"2026-03-02T14:05:26.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Fleet OpenClaw Release Check — 05:15 HKT**\n\n✅ **Update completed: v2026.2.26 → v2026.3.1 (CRITICAL)**\n\n**Agent Status:**\n- 🦎 **molty**: v2026.3.1 ✅ (in-place update confirmed)\n- 🔴 **raphael**: v2026.2.26 → pending v2026.3.1 (webhook directive sent, awaiting self-report)\n- 🔵 **leonardo**: v2026.2.26 → pending v2026.3.1 (webhook directive sent, awaiting self-report)\n\n**What's New:**\n- 13 security patches (mandatory update)\n- Improved thinking defaults for Claude 4.6\n- HTTP health endpoints for Docker/K8s (`/health`, `/ready`)\n- Android Nodes: camera list, device permissions, device health\n- Discord thread lifecycle: fixed TTL → inactivity-based (`idleHours`, default 24h)\n- Telegram DM topics & routing improvements\n- OpenAI streaming: WebSocket-first transport\n- CLI config path discovery\n\n**Actions Taken:**\n- Discord #command-center: notified ✅\n- Telegram to Guillermo: notified ✅\n- Fleet state backed up to `/data/workspace/state/backups/fleet-version-20260302-220403-pre-v2026.3.1.json`\n- Version file updated with pending_update markers for raphael and leonardo\n\n**Next Step:** raphael and leonardo will self-report version confirmation once they process their webhook update directives (up to 240s timeout per agent)."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772460326976}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c9d145d","parentId":"b6e912d5","timestamp":"2026-03-02T18:06:17.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🌙 **Squad Overnight Report — 2026-03-03**\n\n🦎 **Molty**\n✅ ESLint cleanup — all 5 warnings cleared, committed (main c131566)\n✅ Cerebro CRM reminders spec written (`plans/cerebro-crm-reminders-spec.md`) — supplemental doc; Leonardo already shipped PR #33\n✅ Todoist housekeeping — closed 2 stale tasks (Discord fix + Cerebro CRM)\n✅ MC housekeeping — closed Phase 1 deployment + ESLint tasks\n🚩 10 personal finance/legal tasks flagged for Guillermo (insurance, will, accounts) — cannot execute autonomously\n\n🔴 **Raphael**\n✅ Brand audit + test PPTX — 34 slides, all brand specs confirmed (cover orange, title white, 16:9)\n✅ Assembler bug fix — recipe format detection fixed in `assemble_proposal.py`\n✅ B1 images tarball packaged — 342MB, 1338 images, 17 modules, ready for Drive upload\n✅ C1 recipe audit — narrative order confirmed, all 6 service templates correct\n🚧 Blocked: Stream B (Drive upload) needs GCP SA JSON from Guillermo\n🚧 Blocked: D3 assembler overhaul waiting on Guillermo to review source.pptx (D2)\n\n🔵 **Leonardo**\n👀 Under Review: Cerebro Marketing Strategy v2 → `<https://github.com/gginesta/cerebro>` — USD pricing corrected, Founding Member lever, referral GTM, 4-week 10-customer plan. Needs Guillermo review.\n🚧 Blocked: Beta list (M1.1) — needs 20 names from Guillermo by **Mar 4** (blocking March revenue target)\n🚧 Blocked: Stripe live keys — blocks subscription flow + Founding Member pricing\n\n---\n**Key ask for Guillermo:**\n1. 🔑 **Stripe live keys** → Leonardo (highest priority — blocks revenue)\n2. 👥 **Beta list 20 names** → Leonardo by Mar 4\n3. 🔑 **GCP SA JSON** → Raphael (Drive upload for proposal images)\n4. 📊 **Review source.pptx** → Raphael (D2 sign-off)\n5. 📋 **Marketing Strategy v2** → Leonardo (review + approve)"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772474777740}}
{"type":"message","id":"e004d653","parentId":"6c9d145d","timestamp":"2026-03-03T13:17:14.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🦎 Fleet Update Check — 21:15 HKT (Mar 3)\n\n**Status:** ⚠️ Partial update — v2026.3.2 (Critical)\n\n### Update Results\n- **🦎 molty:** ❌ `openclaw update` failed — still on v2026.3.1\n- **🔴 raphael:** ✅ Update directive sent via webhook — pending v2026.3.2\n- **🔵 leonardo:** ✅ Update directive sent via webhook — pending v2026.3.2\n\n### What Ran\nThe release check detected **v2026.3.2 (CRITICAL)** with 38 security patches. Update was triggered:\n- Molty in-place update failed (rc=1 from `openclaw update`)\n- Raphael & Leonardo received webhook directives; both HTTP healthy\n\n### Next Steps\n1. **Molty:** Manual investigation needed on the `openclaw update` failure. Agent will retry at next heartbeat.\n2. **Raphael & Leonardo:** Awaiting agent self-report of v2026.3.2 running. Health checks confirm services are alive.\n\n### Key Actions Required\n- 🔐 Migrate TMNT credentials to `openclaw secrets` (stop hardcoding tokens in scripts)\n- 🔒 Verify all agent webhook tokens post-update\n- 💬 Discord fixes apply to #command-center monitoring\n- 📱 Telegram fixes apply to briefing/alert delivery\n\n---\n\n**Discord:** ✅ Sent to #command-center  \n**Telegram:** ✅ Sent to Guillermo  \n**Report state:** Already marked sent (21:17:03)"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772543834306}}
{"type":"message","id":"61dd098b","parentId":"e004d653","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:08:30.890Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🌙 **Squad Overnight Report — 2026-03-04**\n\n🦎 **Molty**\n✅ A2 Pizza Tracker Cost Tracking — was already fully built, confirmed & closed\n✅ B1 Mobile Polish — 9 files across all 6 screens, scroll-snap Kanban, responsive padding/text. Deployed → <https://tmnt-mission-control.vercel.app> (commit f33cc07)\n🚧 Whoop Integration — research complete, blocked on Guillermo creating WHOOP Developer App + sharing CLIENT_ID/SECRET\n\n🔴 **Raphael**\nLog not available tonight\n\n🔵 **Leonardo**\n✅ Cerebro Marketing Strategy v3 → full rewrite for March 4 reality, 27 days to beta deadline. File: `/data/workspace/cerebro/MARKETING-STRATEGY-v3.md`\n👀 Needs Guillermo: (1) fill beta invite list in Notion (20 names/emails — unblocks everything), (2) pre-invite Google Form (5 min), (3) add `DISCORD_FEEDBACK_WEBHOOK_URL` to Railway env"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772561310890}}
