{"type":"message","id":"5be0a922","parentId":"fa737997","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:42:21.356Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The services are running but require auth on the /health endpoint. That's new behavior - perhaps after the v2026.3.x updates. But the webhooks should still work with the correct token...\n\nLet me check if the webhook is timing out or actually returning 502. Maybe the gateways are stuck processing something.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Services are up but gateways aren't responding to webhooks (502 timeout). This could be:\n1. Gateway processes hung/stuck\n2. Container resource limits hit\n3. Post-update config issue\n\n**Immediate fix:** Guillermo, can you trigger a Railway redeploy on both:\n- `ggv-raphael` \n- `leonardo-production`\n\nThat should restart their gateway processes. I'll also check their Discord channels to see if they've posted anything recently."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01RpeGSfTzD4612bhNcdVWg2","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"read","channel":"discord","target":"1468164139674238976","limit":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":293,"cacheRead":81303,"cacheWrite":221,"totalTokens":81825,"cost":{"input":0.00004,"output":0.007325000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0406515,"cacheWrite":0.00138125,"total":0.049397750000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773394933604}}
