{"type":"message","id":"b515f0b0","parentId":"a694d4d7","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:42:33.174Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - Raphael last posted on Mar 13 at 09:31 HKT (about 8 hours ago). His Discord is working. The webhook seems to be the issue. But both agents are returning 502 on webhook calls while Discord is working. Let me check Leonardo too and then report what I found.\n\nIt looks like:\n1. Discord is working for both (Raphael posted earlier today)\n2. The webhook endpoint is returning 502 (gateway not responding)\n3. Their overnight crons didn't produce logs\n\nMaybe the issue is their cron jobs aren't configured or they didn't have tasks? Let me check if we have visibility into their cron lists.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Wait — Raphael posted to Discord at 17:31 HKT today (8 hours ago), so his Discord IS working. The webhook endpoint is what's failing (502). Let me try pinging him via Discord instead:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0131gXyXHU6xzPNHWxXe1JZP","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"discord","target":"1468164139674238976","message":"<@1468164929285783644> Status check — why no overnight run last night? Report your cron status and any errors."}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01RraCb4UzC5AsESKRFyCbVc","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"discord","target":"1470919437975814226","message":"<@1470919061763522570> Status check — why no overnight run last night? Report your cron status and any errors."}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":461,"cacheRead":81524,"cacheWrite":3823,"totalTokens":85816,"cost":{"input":0.00004,"output":0.011525,"cacheRead":0.040762,"cacheWrite":0.023893750000000002,"total":0.07622075}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773394941939}}
