{"type":"message","id":"87152676","parentId":"29fa986f","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:42:41.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, both Discord messages sent successfully. So their Discord connections are working, but their webhook endpoints are returning 502. I've sent status check requests via Discord. Let me report to Guillermo.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Paged both via Discord. Their webhooks are returning 502 but Discord is working — they should respond shortly.\n\nPossible causes:\n1. **Cron misconfiguration** — their overnight crons might not be set up correctly\n2. **No tasks in backlog** — nothing to execute\n3. **Gateway stuck** — webhook endpoint unresponsive (502) even though Discord routing works\n\nWill update once they reply. The webhook 502s suggest we should check if their gateway processes need attention — though that wouldn't explain missing overnight logs if their crons fired via internal scheduler."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":180,"cacheRead":85347,"cacheWrite":622,"totalTokens":86157,"cost":{"input":0.00004,"output":0.0045000000000000005,"cacheRead":0.042673499999999996,"cacheWrite":0.0038875000000000003,"total":0.051101}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773394954614}}
