{"type":"message","id":"8a94b8a8","parentId":"3d602812","timestamp":"2026-03-16T13:54:14.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, now I have a clear picture. Let me identify what's stale and needs updating:\n\n**Tasks that should be DONE (Raphael completed these):**\n- A1-A6 (Stream A brand) — All completed by Raphael weeks ago\n- A7 — Raphael just confirmed PASS\n- G2 — Raphael confirmed done tonight\n- G3 — Raphael confirmed done tonight\n- C3, C4, C5, C6 — Raphael completed these (from overnight reports)\n- Stream A parent task — done\n- A1-test — done (part of Stream A)\n\n\n- G4a is under review waiting on Guillermo, while the outreach campaign has Phase 1 wrapped up and Phase 2 actively moving forward. PLAN-016 is slipping and needs rescheduling, and M1.1 might still be in progress with beta selection underway though the form is ready. Let me batch update the clearly stale ones.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Found a lot of stale tasks. Let me batch update them:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0111oUi2vqH1JNhBeHzXeMqW","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"#!/bin/bash\n# Batch update stale MC tasks\n\nMC_API=\"https://resilient-chinchilla-241.convex.site/api/task\"\nMC_KEY=\"Bearer 232e4ddf7d69c31e01ad0fa0a61f70c29e4837ed018a153cce1a429842bb7cbc\"\n\nupdate_task() {\n    local id=\"$1\"\n    local status=\"$2\"\n    local title=\"$3\"\n    curl -s -X PATCH \"$MC_API\" \\\n      -H \"Authorization: $MC_KEY\" \\\n      -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n      -d \"{\\\"id\\\": \\\"$id\\\", \\\"status\\\": \\\"$status\\\"}\" | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print(f'  {d.get(\\\"status\\\",\\\"?\\\")}: {\\\"$title\\\"[:60]}')\" 2>/dev/null\n}\n\necho \"=== Marking Stream A (A1-A6 + parent + A1-test) as DONE ===\"\nupdate_task \"jn73f56re993zr4d0y5fged5fh81ph2e\" \"done\" \"A1: BRAND color dict\"\nupdate_task \"jn713v6rpy79gf4s7nn8hnsvnd81qgb9\" \"done\" \"A2: BRAND font dict